00:49:25.860 --> 00:49:28.010
can be difficult sometimes.

00:49:28.010 --> 00:49:31.740
So what we try to do
in order to simplify

00:49:31.740 --> 00:49:35.950
that is find an equation that
is satisfied by the Heisenberg

00:49:35.950 --> 00:49:40.270
